; PowerTest.gcode - centered on 9500x12000 build plate
; X range: -4750..4750, Y range: -6000..6000
; Eight separate 1900x1900 test squares, 10%..80% power
; Two-layer test

G31 ; Home all chamber items
G32 Z10 ; Prep build chamber - 5 mm (converted in firmware)
M21 ; Turn fan off
M19 ; Request user to insert material
G33 ; Move the bar

M19 ; Request user to insert material

M20 ; Turn fan on

G0 X13500 Y13500 ; Rapid to center origin location
G92 X0 Y0 ; Set current position as centered origin

M57 L1 ; Guide beam off
M58 F100 ; Set scan speed

